-- China Will Publish Results of Foxconn Suicides Probe, Beijing News Says
-- Weiyi Lim
-- 2010-06-13T05:06:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-13/china-will-publish-results-of-foxconn-suicides-probe-beijing-news-says.html

          
          
             China will make public the results
of its investigation into a spate of suicides at Foxconn
Technology Group after it finished investigating the matter,
Beijing News reported, citing Zhang Xiaojian, Vice Minister of
Human Resources and Social Security.  
